"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 199, 103);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/82-X2fHeYuh4iGyNm_9jv.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(240, 199, 103);\">His youngest son, <strong>Prince Calren</strong> - bratty, indulgent, and desperate to be taken seriously - was installed as your co-ruler.</span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 199, 103);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/XYqhSF3WdfUDPRkkO79WS.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(240, 199, 103);\">At his side stood <strong>Lady Bethyn</strong>, beautiful, ruthless, and far more dangerous than her husband.</span></p><p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 199, 103);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/7SjqEAq4SSGVcyy22h8uc.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(240, 199, 103);\">You had one ally in the form of <strong>Lady Serena</strong>, your wife’s former lady-in-waiting and best friend. The two of you became close as you both mourned Alyss.</span></p><p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(240, 199, 103);\">The duchy survived. Thrived.</span></p><p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(240, 199, 103);\">And then everything broke open.</span></p><p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(240, 199, 103);\">A year later, you found Alyss alive.</span></p><p class=\"p1\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/k7f65Bbyj_MkFVCfyFqYh.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(240, 199, 103);\">She was living quietly in the countryside with a commoner named <strong>Brannic 